'''洪錫天'''（{{lang-ko|홍석천}}，{{bd|1971年|2月3日|catIdx=Hong}}）是韓國的藝人、模特兒及演員。 他在2000年9月公開[[出櫃|出櫃]]。<ref>{{cite news |url = http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20130326/00470_001.html |title = 金在中港騷洩蜜 |publisher = 太陽報 |date = 2013-03-25 |accessdate = 2013-12-10 |archive-date = 2020-04-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200418184853/http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20130326/00470_001.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>餐飲副業發展相當成功，曾是擁有11家餐廳的老闆，卻被[[梨泰院|梨泰院]][[2019冠狀病毒病韓國疫情|群爆事件]]而大規模倒閉，截至2021年，只剩一家餐廳依然營業。<ref>{{Cite web|title=[代你旅遊 - 梨泰院] 原來韓國人都不敢去梨泰院?! 疫情下的梨泰院商店70％倒閉?! 韓國人都害怕美軍因為...?! 🐝 Mira 咪拉 - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izgJtewqpkQ|accessdate=2021-01-23|work=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2021-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210809134841/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izgJtewqpkQ&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年，他透露他是NCT成員[[李泰容|泰容]]的遠房親戚。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.allkpop.com/article/2018/01/hong-suk-chun-finally-reveals-the-sm-idol-hes-related-to-is-ncts-taeyong|title=Hong Suk Chun finally reveals the SM idol he's related to is NCT's Taeyong  {{!}} allkpop.com|newspaper=allkpop|accessdate=2018-01-15|archive-date=2019-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821165602/https://www.allkpop.com/article/2018/01/hong-suk-chun-finally-reveals-the-sm-idol-hes-related-to-is-ncts-taeyong|dead-url=no}}</ref>

